nglish the gist of the early Chinese alchemical corpus.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aAlchemyzChinaxHistory. 0aTaoismzChinaxHistory. 4aAsian Studies. 4aHistory -- Asian. 4aReligion -- Asian. 7aRELIGION / Taoism (see also PHILOSOPHY / Taoist).2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804767736zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767736423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767736/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles